Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:05.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)陛下！ パレードへの参列を\Nお取りやめくださいませ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty,\Nplease do not attend the parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:08.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾘｵｽ17世)\Nパレードは予定どおり行う｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The parade will be carried out as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:10.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔どもが邪魔するなら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If the demons mean to interfere,\Nwe will merely slaughter them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:13.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆殺しにするまでだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:15.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)なぜ来ない…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:18.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)悪魔たちが\N何か たくらんでいる｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The demons are scheming something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:20.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正午には パレードの開始だ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The parade will commence at noon.\NWe have to find and stop them before then!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それまでに捜して\N取り押さえなければ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:25.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカーン！\Nドカーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:28.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)\N貴様 なぜ約束の場所に来ない？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you not show up\Nwhere we were supposed to meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:30.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅ･ﾄﾞﾗﾝｺﾞ)\Nだって パレード見てたんだもん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was watching the parade!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:33.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく来い！ もう時間がない！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come! We're out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:36.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここが 魔族どもとの\N決戦の地ということだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we battle the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:38.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドォーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:40.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドォン ドォン ドォン！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:42.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遅かったな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally.\NIt is time we settle this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:46.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかげんに\N決着をつけようではないか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:50.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)俺がヤツらを引き付ける｡\Nドカッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I will draw them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:52.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)お前たちは生きろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:05.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドゴン‼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Mugaro go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:16.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムガロちゃん どこ行ったんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This way? That way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:19.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっち？ あっち？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:21.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ～ どっち？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:00.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)あれは…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:05.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムガロ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mugaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the power the gods seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:10.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが 神の求める力か｡ あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:17.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ～～！\Nガキン！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:03:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rage of Bahamut
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんのつもりだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)この戦いに\N決着をつけてはなりません｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This fight can't be settled like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:33.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余の命を\N狙う悪魔を 逃せというのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you suggesting I let a demon\Nwho is after my life go free?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:45.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様の戯れ言は もう聞き飽きた！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am done listening to your nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I would eliminate you\Nif you interfered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:55.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,邪魔をするなら\N排除すると言ったはずだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:18.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドゴッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,がはっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ があっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This demon will die if I defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:32.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が敗れれば\Nその悪魔は死ぬぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカッ！\Nうっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,三種族の共存を\N諦めないのだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You still believe the three races can\Nlive in peace, do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then try to fight for it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:51.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ならば この場を切り抜けてみよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドスッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドスッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:23.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺せ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦いは終わった｡\N終わってなどいない！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:32.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 この場で死ぬ意味は\Nないはずだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be no reason\Nfor you to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムガロ！\Nあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mugaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドサッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, are you injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:03.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(隊長)陛下 おケガは？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So they show themselves. Contemptible gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:06.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり現れたか 神め｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Mugaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫どこ行くの!? ムガロちゃん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn into a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:36.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)竜になれ！\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナ 竜になるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:42.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,竜って…｡ 何？ 急に｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We need your power now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:45.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今こそ お前の力が必要なんだ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムガロを…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to save Mugaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:50.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち魔族を助けてくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to save the demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:38.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメ 無理！ 変身できない！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working! I can't transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:49.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何よ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:53.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガン！\Nうっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:10.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)ちくしょう～～～‼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rage of Bahamut
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rag Demon has finally been caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:17.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(市民)包帯悪魔\Nとうとう捕まったか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(市民)\Nさすがは シャリオス様だな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,King Charioce did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:22.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(市民)\Nそれにしても 騎士団の団長が➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe a knight captain\Nwas aiding the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:25.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔に加担してたなんて\Nとんでもねぇな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:28.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(市民)オルレアン騎士団ってのも\N落ちたもんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How far the Orleans Knights have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:30.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(市民)\N私 この団長 見かけたことあるよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen the captain before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵隊さん\Nこのニーナって子は 間違いだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, there's gotta be some sort of mistake\Nwith this girl Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな大層なことが\Nできる子じゃあねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not someone who could do anything\Nlike this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:40.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだよ｡ ニーナは いつも元気で\Nとってもいい子なんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Nina's such a good,\Ncheerful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ そうだ！\N(ﾊﾟﾝ屋)昨日だって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When I put her on my shoulders yesterday\Nso she could see the parade better,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が肩車して\Nパレードを見せてやったら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:47.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きゃっきゃと喜んでたんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,she was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she attacked the king after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:51.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのあとに\N王様を襲ったなんて ありえねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:54.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ 頼むよ｡\N兵隊さんから もう一度➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, could you talk to the king\Nand ask him to look into it one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:57.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王様に調べるように言ってくれ…｡\Nおっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you defend this traitor any more,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:59.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(兵士)\Nそれ以上 反逆者をかばうなら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll throw you all into prison too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:01.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様らも牢にぶち込むぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What did they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:12.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)何やってんのよ あの子たち｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The drunk and the duck\Nhave run off too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:16.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,酔っ払いとアヒルも\Nどっか行っちゃうし｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now read the charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:21.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(重臣)\Nこれより 罪状を読み上げる｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:25.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢被告人 カイザル･リドファルド｡\N被告は 陛下を守護する➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the accused, Kaisar Lidfard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been accused of consorting with demons
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:30.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オルレアン騎士団長でありながら\N悪魔と密会を行うこと数度｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,while having sworn to protect His Majesty\Nas captain of the Orleans Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:34.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パレードにおいては\N反逆者たちの蛮行に加担｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You aided the rebels with their attack on the parade,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and together with the Rag Demon,\Nraised your sword against His Majesty,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:38.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,包帯悪魔と共に\N陛下へ刃を向ける暴挙には➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:41.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もはや 弁解の余地なし｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,for which there can be no justification!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-These are crimes against the sovereign.\N-What did he want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:43.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,国家への犯意ありとみなし｣…｡\N(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)あの人➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:47.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体 何がしたかったんすかね？\N(重臣)｢国家反逆罪を適用する｣！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are hereby charged with treason!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use. I'm not getting excited at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(心の声)\N≪ダメだ ドキドキしない≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The accused, Nina Drango.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:59.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(重臣)｢被告人 ニーナ･ドランゴ｣｡\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:03.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(重臣)｢被告人は 人でありながら\N悪魔の危険思想に染まり➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You are accused of sympathizing with\Ndangerous demon ideology despite being human,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:06.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パレードにおいての襲撃に加担｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and, additionally, aiding in the parade attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:09.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また ここ数日のうちに\N現れたとされる➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also suspicions of your connection
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with a red dragon\Nthat has emerged in the last few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,赤い竜との関係性も疑わしく➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:15.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,反乱分子であることは\N明白である｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is evident you are a member of the rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:19.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よって 被告人にも\N国家反逆罪を適用する｣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you will also\Nbe charged with treason!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:25.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,陛下 判決をお願いいたします｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, your judgment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:27.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いします｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Imprison both in the prison tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:32.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,両名を牢獄島において\N無期の刑に処する｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,where they will be held indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ!? 無期？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Indefinitely?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:36.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,連れていけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:43.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ ちょ… やだ｡\N待って 待って 待って 待って！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No! Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:45.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無期って… うそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Indefinitely? You've gotta be kidding!\NCould you make it more like three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:47.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３日くらいにして｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Indefinitely is way too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:52.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無期って あんまりだよ～｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ！\N待て｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:11.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何見てんのよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:16.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言っとくけど 私 あんたのこと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're a good king or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:19.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全然 いい王様だなんて\N思ってないんだから｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:23.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王様は みんなに優しくしなきゃ\Nいけないんじゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't the king have to be nice to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Picking on folks because they're demons,\Nputting collars on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:27.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔だからって\Nいじめて 首輪なんか着けて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,hurting them to make them do what you say-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うこと聞かせようと\N傷つけたりして！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,do you really think that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことしていいと\N思ってるの!? うっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:36.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王都の工事だって\N悪魔に手伝ってもらってるくせに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When this whole capital was built by demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当は 悪魔の力が必要なくせに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When actually you need them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you just kill them\Nwithout a thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,簡単に殺そうとするなんて！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:47.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたのやってることは\Nただの弱い者いじめよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but a big bully!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなは あなたのこと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says you're a great king\Nwho made the capital rich,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:52.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王都を繁栄させた\N偉大な王様だって言うけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's all a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:57.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなのうそ！\Nあんたは ただの悪い王様だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just an evil king!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:14:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A worthless king who just sits on his throne,\Npicking on the weak demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:14:00.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弱い悪魔をいじめて\N威張って ふんぞり返ってる➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:03.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメな王様だ！\N(兵士)ぐっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans and demons may be scared of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:07.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人も悪魔も あなたにおびえて\N怖がってるけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:09.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は 違う｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the least bit scared of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:12.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたなんか\Nち～っとも怖くないんだから！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:25.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何笑ってんのよ｡\N(兵士)くっ… いいかげん 黙れ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth al-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:28.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ！ あ痛たたたっ！ ああっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the red dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:33.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は\N赤い竜なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I have no idea what you're referring to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:35.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違います｡\N何をおっしゃっているのか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かりません｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:48.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,連れていけ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(兵士)立て！\Nやめて｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get up!\N-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come on!\N-That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:52.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(兵士)ほら｡\N痛い！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:18.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)ガブリエル様\N気が付いたようです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The child is awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶﾞﾌﾞﾘｴﾙ)\Nおびえることはありません｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:25.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここにいる神たちは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,are all on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:28.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆 あなたの仲間なのですよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is El.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたの名前は エル｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:42.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたの母ジャンヌ･ダルクが\Nあなたに授けた名前です｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the name your mother Jeanne D'Arc\Ngave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:47.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さんに\N会いたくはないですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not wish to see your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not wish to save your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:51.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さんを\N助けたくはないですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:53.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちと力を合わせれば➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you join forces with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:56.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お母さんに会うことができますよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be able to meet your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:09.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)クワッ！ クワァ～｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クワァ～！\Nドン！ ドンドン！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:16.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)クワァ～！\N≫(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)やめとけ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd we have to return to heaven this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:20.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)こんな形で\N神の国に戻ってくるなんて！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:22.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき ソフィエル様に➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have told Lady Sofiel about Mugaro\Nwhen we had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:24.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムガロのことを\N言えばよかったんですよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:27.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)ふんっ｡\N≪(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)ハンサの言うとおりだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamsa is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:34.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ソフィエル様！ どうクワァ\N私たちの軟禁をお解きください｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Sofiel! Please let us free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We planned to tell you that this was the child you\Nwere seeking once we gathered enough evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:36.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの少年が例の子供であると➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:40.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,十分な証拠を得てから\N伝えるつもりだったのです｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:44.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決して\N謀反の意志などございません！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I assure you we had no intention of betraying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:48.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)なぜ あの子供を隠した？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you hide the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:52.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,答えろ！\Nクワァ～…｡ クワッ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I just felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:56.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんとなくだ｡\N(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)なんとなく？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You just felt like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:59.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう意味だ？\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)意味なんてねぇよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:03.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)バカなのか お前は｡\N(ﾊﾝｻ)ほんとにバカです！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And what are you looking to start with that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:05.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)\Nお前らこそ あのガキを使って➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:09.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を始める気だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans have lost their way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:13.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)ガブリエル様は\N信仰心を失った人間たちが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and Lady Gabriel wishes to guide them\Nback to offering their prayers to the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再び 神のみもとに\N祈りをささげるよう➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:18.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,導くことをお考えだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll be using the kid for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:22.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)\Nそれに あいつを利用するのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The child's power is the only thing capable of\Nbreaking the forbidden magic used by humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの子供の力は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:29.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間たちが使う\N禁じられた術を破る唯一の力だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:32.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)くっ｡\Nあんな子供を巻き込むな！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the kid out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be Jeanne D'Arc all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:36.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌ･ダルクの\N二の舞になるぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You overstep your bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:39.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,口が過ぎるぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:42.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)クワァ～…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,も… 申し訳ございません\Nソフィエル様｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A thousand apologies, Lady Sofiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,酒がないもので\Nちょっとイライラしてるんです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a little irritated\Nbecause he hasn't had his drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:52.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)お前たちが 任務を\N妨害したことに変わりはない｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact remains that you interfered with our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:55.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらく ここで頭を冷やせ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You would do well to think about\Nwhat you've done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:57.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クワァ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:18:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:01.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々は なんという\N運命なんでしょうクワァ？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you backed the humans too much on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:04.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人に肩入れし過ぎたんじゃ\Nないですクワァ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:07.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせぇ｡\N(ﾊﾝｻ)そういえば➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me. When we were teleporting away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:10.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちが魔法陣に消えるとき➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the young lady was yelling from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地上で\Nお嬢さんが叫んでましたね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's happened to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:20.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)どうしてますクワァね｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無事だといいんですけど…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:29.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(船頭)ほ～ら 見えてきたぞ｡\Nあれが お前の新居だ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなか立派だろう？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:38.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脱出不可能な\N難攻不落の地下牢獄なんだぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an impregnable and unescapable\Nunderground dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:41.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おじさん 包帯悪魔はどうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened to the Rag Demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:45.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(船頭)ああ～ 今頃は たっぷりと\N拷問を受けてるだろうよ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably getting tortured as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to get him to spill about who else\Nis working with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:48.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他に仲間がいないか\N吐かせるためにな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ…｡\N(船頭)おい｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't talk to the prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:53.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,罪人と口を利くなよ！\Nあっ!?➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:56.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろ｡ 誰も見てねぇし\Nかまわねぇだろ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? Nobody's even around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always getting worked up about nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おめぇ いっつも細けぇんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:02.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ごめんね アザゼル≫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Azazel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:05.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪あのとき\N私が竜になれていたら…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I was able to transform into a dragon, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:15.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バチン！(ﾑﾁでたたく音)\N(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)ああっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just spill it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:24.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかげん 吐いたらどうだ？\Nおりゃあ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where your base is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(兵士)アジトの場所を言え！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:31.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おりゃあ～！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:34.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひひひひっ｡ あっ｡\N≪コツ コツ コツ…(足音)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How unsightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:45.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶざまだな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は\Nあの神が連れ去った子供が➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know what the taken child was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何者か知っていたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You really had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:01.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知らずに連れ歩いていたのか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まぬけなヤツだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:15.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(囚人)ひ～っひひひっ｡\N(囚人)なんだよ｡ ええっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:20.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(囚人)見るな｡\N(囚人)なんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:33.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ！ 痛たたっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods were desperate to get the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの子供を手に入れるために➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:06.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神は 躍起になっていた｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:09.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神の手に渡る前に\N殺すつもりだったが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I planned to kill the child\Nbefore he fell into their hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but you ruined it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:12.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前たちのせいで台なしだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:16.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあいい｡ あの子供を手に入れ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The gods are overconfident now that they\Nhave the child. So I will simply kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:20.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,調子に乗った神もろとも\N亡き者にしてやる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:26.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすれば さすがに\Nあの女も祈ることをやめるだろう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that woman will surely stop praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:28.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢あの女｣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The former saint...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かつての聖女➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:38.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンヌ･ダルクだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeanne...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,D'Arc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay\NI cast the usual spell
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:22:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stagnation, stagnation\NMy words and heart are at odds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Default\NI've taken all the paint
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And mixed up all the colors\NUntil you're left with me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So fragile\NYet strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Close to overflowing\NBut not spilling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm incomplete\NI won't amount to much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.97,0:22:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a good luck charm\NI'm not asking for your help
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a good luck charm\NI was just clinging to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end it all today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done living this pointless life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end it all today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken my last, pointless breath
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To whom it may concern, see ya and goodbye\NI killed the person I was yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.79,0:22:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To whom it may concern, see ya and goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.38,0:23:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A new morning is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.11,0:23:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:17.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(看守)さっさと入れ！\N(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)うわっ あたっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:19.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガシャン
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really have to be so rough?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:22.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと ましな扱いは\Nできないのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.24,0:23:27.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:31.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪これは また\Nとんだ騎士様のご登場だ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. If it isn't the great and noble knight,\Ngracing us with his presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:35.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪もっと周りを見ろって\Nいつも言ってんだろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.50,0:23:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you to pay more attention\Nto your surroundings, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.84,0:23:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.64,0:23:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's the aristocrat, Kaisar!\N- Demon Azazel here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- I challenge you to a battle!\N- Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.60,0:23:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Rage of Bahamut:\NVirgin Soul, "Same Old. Same Old."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ready!\N- Rock, Paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- R-r-ro-rock!\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.15,0:24:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Baha Soul!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Baha Baha Bahasoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.37,0:24:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You there.\NYou must watch next time too, understood?
